text: Choi Won-jae (Hangul: 최원재, born October 26, 1993), better known by his stage name Kid Milli (Hangul: 키드밀리), is a South Korean rapper. He released his first extended play, Maiden Voyage, on February 23, 2017. == Biography == Before becoming a rapper, Kid Milli was a StarCraft pro-gamer.
